	function keepalive() {
		$.post('fireflyweb.aspx?prgname=StayConnect',{},function(e){ });
	}

    	
	window.onpageshow = function(event) {
		if (event.persisted) {
			$('.Loading').hide();
		}
	};
  $(document).ready(function(e){
	$('ul.nav li.dropdown > a').click(function(e){
		$(this).parent().children('ul').toggle();
	});
